Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:03.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the fourth day of the Grand Magic Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,in one of the battle part's tag matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:09.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a showdown between four \NDragon Slayers is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:14.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Natsu and Gajeel vs. Sting and Rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The battle against the Twin \NDragons of Sabertooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:24.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a battle that puts Fairy Tail's bond and \Npride on the line, has begun at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Clam it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wha...?! Hey! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:01.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can take both of you on by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, attack me at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:18.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! Now Natsu Dragneel of Fairy Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:21.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is challenging the two of them to a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're fired up, ain'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu vs. the Twin Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What happened to Gajeel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gray-sama! You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although Natsu is the one who's fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rogue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:44.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun! The fight's just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It feels like Zeref,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but it's different somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the stadium again, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jellal! Don't let him get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:18.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know! I'm concerned about \Nthe match, but right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can take us on by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just messin' with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have no business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me fight Gajeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You want Gajeel, you gotta go through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon Force is the power of a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:40.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more powerful in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe your power's half-baked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's happening with the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu and Gajeel are winnin', of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I understand if you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but it's your job to rest up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and regain your strength and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Knowing Natsu-san, I'm \Nsure he'll be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:22.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're so tough, they should have a plaque \Nwith that word hanging on a wall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Carla for you! You're a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My power is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:42.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the power I used to kill Vicelogia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. Then I'll use my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...to fight for my friends \Nwho were laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look out, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Roar of the Shadow Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Frosch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeesh. That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at that gleeful mug...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Those two definitely aren't weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:47.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but Natsu responds to stronger opponents by \Nbecoming more powerful than he already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,His opponents are tough, \Ntoo. They don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both sides are quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Marvelous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That guy's a blockhead, but when it comes \Nto fighting, his mind is a steel trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wonderful parfum, Natsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:15.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn, how strong is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But where did Gajeel go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of what'll happen \Nwhen he comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:40.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have no memory of seeing the power of \Nthe Dragon Force losing ground like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:43.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Power, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please let me be your disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:07:00.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I saw your fight before! \NI wanna get strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:03.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wanna get strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A cat disciple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:46.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This feeling... The quality of \Nthe magic has changed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The magic of those two has begun to merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, I wasn't able to get strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:58.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I love watching strong Sting-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unison Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Their will, breathing, and magic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,have combined perfectly into one power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu! Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rogue, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun, you're the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are walls that power \Nalone can't break through...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yajima-san, what the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unison Raid. It's so-called Uniting Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:48.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's high level magic that \Nin general can't be mastered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:51.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,even if you devote your whole life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the power of the Twin Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Shadow Dragon Fang Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not moving! He intends to take it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Happy, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You here to see him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'll see ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:34.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:58.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Fiore's strongest guild, Sabertooth, vs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the strongest guild seven \Nyears ago, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And taking the challenge of this \Ntag battle are four dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although one of them has \Ngone off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Currently, below the arena,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu and the Twin Dragons \Nare locked in fierce battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's become quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:19.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No... I feel a strange pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yo. How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. Is your match next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I'll win it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have ever since I joined the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, \N"pressure"? That's pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing, a \Nhusband-and-wife comedy routine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We ain't married!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter how far away he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,he'll always be watching over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:17.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're surrounded by such good children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are walls that can't be \Nbroken through power alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But if there is a power that \Ncan break through those walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Shadow Dragon Fang Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...the power of feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Secret Dragon Slayer Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crimson Lotus Exploding Flame Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! It looks like the mega-moves \Nof both sides ended the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like an earthquake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the live feed lacrima is \Nexperiencing technical difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so please sit tight a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't feel any magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Meaning it's settled...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Thank you for your patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems Lacrima-Vision is back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu Dragneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your power is... immeasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lector...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:39.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The last one standing is Natsu Dragneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A guild is a place that nurtures feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:04.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Fairy Tail! He broke the Twin Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The winner is Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With this, they've leaped to first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And this brings an end to the fourth \Nday of the Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:20.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After one day off, we'll be back the day \Nafter tomorrow with the final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The last day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...will feature a survival battle, \Nwith all of the members participating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Which guild will achieve victory in the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:31.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't anyone miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I figured it would turn out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:40.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what I expected, \NI guess I should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Our goal for the final day has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Defeat Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're mine, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Laxus... Makarov-dono's grandchild...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun, Natsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lector...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe those two lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was an interesting match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've thoroughly memorized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This'll keep us in the spotlight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:34.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"For a while"... If they have a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Saber's master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The power of feelings, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. I'll give this match to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After this one, we're \Ngonna keep winning anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna miss one or two points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:07.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't cry about that one point later, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's fight again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Total defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:28.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If Gajeel has the same \Nfighting strength as Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:34.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just how arrogant am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You did it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I gotta hurry up and tell Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You did it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Today, I'll give you honest praise, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't be modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:59.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You gave us a good show, but \Nwhat happened to Gajeel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:06.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He took off during the middle of it! Doesn't \Nhe know the meaning of "tag battle"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:10.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what you did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:17.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get plenty of rest tomorrow to prepare \Nfor the final day's survival battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The final battle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Victory first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After that, I'm gonna fight \Nyou two, Erza and Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you're putting the horse \Nbefore the carriage or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna ask how it turned out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I already said, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've believed in you since \NI first joined the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:54.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But it ain't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:00.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Our aim is winning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! We've made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although we were off to a rotten start \Nin last place on the first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We were even booed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And laughed at and we got frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But now we're one step away from victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like Natsu said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're gonna turn it around from zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:23.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said to save our tears for when we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:27.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right! Let's climb to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:30.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Give up" ain't in our vocabulary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aim for the 30 million jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not what it's about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:41.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's aim to be the number \None guild in Fiore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:47.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A lot's happened since I joined the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I'm so glad I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is what Fairy Tail is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:40.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Salamander... You're dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:46.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where the hell am I? Under the arena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A dragon... graveyard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jellal, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he got away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No. I put some distance \Nbetween us, and I'm on his trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking I'll make my move where \Nthere aren't any other people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You possess magic similar to Zeref's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So Sabertooth's been defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...by Natsu-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You must have mixed \Nfeelings, Sergeant Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No. I no longer feel any \Nattachment to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That aside, I just can't get used \Nto being addressed as "Sergeant".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Participating in the Eclipse Project...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:52.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...requires a temporary rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Eclipse Project...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:01.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If my power may be of use, then I'm \Nprepared to wield it to the utmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For the sake of Arcadios-sama, \Ntoo, who invited me to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should refer to him as "Colonel".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:15.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I call him "Captain" myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And his old friends call him "Dio".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:25.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But he's socially awkward, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though he's trying to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:31.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,no one is aware of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:49.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Again, that premonition \Nof the castle in ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lu-chan, he did it, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We brought you a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If we keep it up, we might \Nactually win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:04.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Naturally! There's no way \Nthose members can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:08.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?! After seeing today's battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I can't even imagine us losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:14.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you seen Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet he's off chowin' \Ndown on iron somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:24.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll be back sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:35.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That day, we believed in victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:39.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The final day was a really \Nhard-fought battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:43.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you remember it, Lu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:48.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...July 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:55.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We lost... to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That person died...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:09.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That one, too... Even though I loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:16.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't express in words...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:18.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:21.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:24.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:31.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:37.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm revealing my identity. \NNow you reveal yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:45.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:09.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again!
